  <h2>Sensitivity Analysis</h2>
  <p>Our base case uses {growthRatePhase1 * 100}% growth and {discountRate * 100}% discount rate. But reasonable people disagree on these numbers. Here's what the intrinsic value looks like under different assumptions.</p>

